data.description: Fantastic attached unit with a single family home feel… there’s nothing like it! Located in Otay Ranch – one of the newer, quieter, and classier areas of Chula Vista – this 3-bedroom 2½-bathroom beauty will take your breath away. A two-level end unit on a private street, it features one of the larger available floor plans with a variety of upgrades. The front door leads to a cozy living room, with a wood laminate floor that extends to the kitchen. There you will find granite counters, stainless steel appliances, an island counter with a deep double bowl sink, modern cabinets, and a beautifully tiled backsplash wall. The ground level features a half bathroom. The carpeted stairway leads to the second level, also carpeted, where you will find a spacious loft area that could be used as a home office, and a compact laundry closet behind two wide doors. The master suite includes a private bathroom, and opens to its very own balcony overlooking the property’s private back yard, while the two bedrooms share a bathroom. The yard is perfect for outdoor entertaining, barbecuing, family get-togethers, or all of the above! There is also an attached garage for two vehicles, plus ample open parking in the community’s parking areas. Your fabulous future home has access to a resort-style clubhouse, which includes a gym, Olympic-size pool, and hot tub. A nearby trail leads to Sunset View Park, which offers two basketball courts, a playground, and is also suitable for picnics. Plus, just a short drive away, you will find all the shopping and dining options you could ever need, before even reaching the nearby traffic-free SR-125 toll road, which is also a short drive away.
